data.description:
Don’t miss this! Rare, tastefully updated 1-story home close to everything! From the moment you approach the inviting, red front door, you can feel the love and attention that went into the home… Hardwoods throughout; a combination of charming new and original. Living room features tons of light spilling in the new windows which were replaced throughout! Spacious, designer kitchen with all the extras > Granite tops, gorgeous, eye-catching tile backsplash, stainless appliances, including gas range & cooktop - refrigerator stays. Generous space for dining area! 
3 beds and 1.5 updated baths round out this incredible home. Doors to deck lead to backyard oasis with palm trees and fully fenced yard. Spacious storage space/laundry off carport. Hurry!
